00:12:02,542 --> 00:12:07,834
Now those who want your Guru Principle to be awakened
现在那些想要你们的导师原理被唤醒的人

162
00:12:08,041 --> 00:12:11,208
must know that you should not ask for comfort.
要知道你们不应该要求舒适

163
00:12:11,542 --> 00:12:14,750
Even for a thing like that, yesterday you saw the dancing,
即便是一件像那样的事 昨天我看见你们在跳舞

164
00:12:14,959 --> 00:12:17,542
one has to do real tapasya.
你要做真正的苦行

165
00:12:17,959 --> 00:12:19,792
Intensive tapasya you have to do,
集中的苦行你们要修

166
00:12:19,999 --> 00:12:24,583
you cannot learn even a thing like dancing
你没法学会哪怕是一件事 像跳舞

167
00:12:24,875 --> 00:12:28,792
without going into a penance about it.
如果没有做关于它的苦行

168
00:12:29,208 --> 00:12:34,041
So a guru has to go through all penances is important.
所以一个导师要通过所有的苦行 非常重要

169
00:12:34,458 --> 00:12:39,250
Sahaja Yogi need not go, but a guru Sahaja Yogi has to do it.
霎哈嘉瑜伽仕不需要做 但是一个导师型的霎哈嘉瑜伽仕就需要做苦行

170
00:12:39,625 --> 00:12:41,583
We have to have penances,
我们一定要有苦行

171
00:12:41,792 --> 00:12:46,000
and the penance can be any kind of desire you have.
而这苦行可以是任何一种你渴望的

172
00:12:46,208 --> 00:12:48,625
Say, supposing you are very fond of food,
假定 假设你非常喜欢事物

173
00:12:48,917 --> 00:12:53,667
just don't eat the food that you want to eat.
那就不吃你喜欢吃的事物

174
00:12:54,000 --> 00:12:56,250
If you are very fond of sweet food,
如果你非常喜欢甜食

175
00:12:56,542 --> 00:13:01,417
then eat something very bitter, raised to power hundred and eight.
那就吃一些非常苦的108次方

176
00:13:02,208 --> 00:13:08,083
And if you are fond of some sort of a very ...
如果你喜欢一些类型的

177
00:13:08,917 --> 00:13:11,041
- as Indians are, sometimes -
就像印度人 有些时候

178
00:13:11,250 --> 00:13:16,542
... very spicy food then eat so bland the food, without salt.
非常辣的事物 那就吃一些白味的食物 没有盐的那种

179
00:13:16,999 --> 00:13:19,250
Teach your tongue to behave itself.
教你的舌头去自己守规矩

180
00:13:19,542 --> 00:13:23,709
It doesn't behoove a guru to put his attention to food.
一个导师没有必要把他的注意力放在食物上

181
00:13:23,917 --> 00:13:27,792
I have seen some of the Sahaja Yogis, they are all right
我见过一些霎哈嘉瑜伽练习者 他们挺好的

182
00:13:28,000 --> 00:13:30,458
when the food is there, quite concentrated,
当食物在那的时候 非常专注

183
00:13:30,667 --> 00:13:34,125
but when it comes to the programme they have no concentration.
但是当到活动中他们就不专心了

184
00:13:34,333 --> 00:13:39,583
Is a sad thing, such people cannot be gurus. They can be cooks, good,
这是非常难过的 这样的人没法做导师 他们可以做厨师 很好

185
00:13:42,583 --> 00:13:46,500
or could be food-tasters or something like that.
或者可以做美食家 或者就像那样的一些

186
00:13:46,834 --> 00:13:50,041
Will suit them better, but if they have to be gurus
会很适合他们 但是如果他们要做导师

187
00:13:50,250 --> 00:13:54,792
they must learn to control their tongue and their desires.
他们就必须学会控制他们的舌头和他们的欲望

188
00:13:55,583 --> 00:13:59,583
I mean, fasting is a good thing for Sahaja Yogis, fasting is very good.
我的意思是 禁食对于霎哈嘉瑜伽练习者来说是非常好的事 禁食非常好

189
00:13:59,792 --> 00:14:02,333
All the time they are worried, what are we going to have for lunch,
他们总是在担忧 我们中午要吃什么

190
00:14:02,583 --> 00:14:04,542
what are we going to have for dinner?
我们晚餐要吃什么

191
00:14:04,750 --> 00:14:08,583
Such people cannot have their Guru Principle awakened,
这样的人他们的导师原理不能被唤醒

192
00:14:08,917 --> 00:14:13,041
neither they can be gurus. So please be careful.
他们也没法成为导师 所以请注意

193
00:14:13,458 --> 00:14:17,125
The guru must have control over the tongue.
导师一定要控制他们的舌头

194
00:14:17,583 --> 00:14:20,417
He must know when to get angry
他必须知道什么时候要生气

195
00:14:20,625 --> 00:14:24,083
and when to be gentle.
什么时候要温和

196
00:14:24,834 --> 00:14:29,834
He must know what to say when,
他必须知道什么时候要说些什么

197
00:14:30,041 --> 00:14:32,750
how much to say.
要说多少

198
00:14:33,083 --> 00:14:38,625
That's why many gurus have been more effective by not speaking.
这就是为什么很多导师通过沉默为了更加有效果

199
00:14:38,959 --> 00:14:43,542
Silence is the best way you can help others,
沉默是帮助他人的最好方式

200
00:14:43,875 --> 00:14:47,583
but when it comes to explaining Sahaja Yoga, you should speak.
但是当要解释霎哈嘉瑜伽的时候 你就要说

201
00:14:47,875 --> 00:14:50,750
But I have seen with some people they are very eloquent
但是我见过一些人 他们非常雄辩

202
00:14:50,959 --> 00:14:53,166
when it comes to nonsensical things,
当说起无聊的事情的时候

203
00:14:53,375 --> 00:14:55,333
but when it comes to Sahaja Yoga, they don't know anything
但是当要说霎哈嘉瑜伽 他们啥都不知道

204
00:14:55,542 --> 00:14:57,041
about Sahaja Yoga.
关于霎哈嘉瑜伽

205
00:14:57,250 --> 00:14:58,875
So you have to be the master of Sahaja Yoga,
因此你要成为霎哈嘉瑜伽的精通者

206
00:14:59,083 --> 00:15:00,667
if you have to be a Guru,
如果你要成为一个导师

207
00:15:00,875 --> 00:15:04,417
not only in talking, but in your behaviour, in everything.
不只是在言谈上 还要在你的行为上 在所有的事情中

208
00:15:04,625 --> 00:15:09,458
And the karamat
而这karamat

209
00:15:09,875 --> 00:15:11,750
is the ...
就是

210
00:15:11,999 --> 00:15:15,333
I don't know if you use charismatic-word, charismatic they call it
我不知道你是否会用神赐的词 他们称它神赐于能力的

211
00:15:15,583 --> 00:15:19,291
or you say, the one how to do it
或者你可以说 那个怎样做

212
00:15:19,750 --> 00:15:23,375
how to raise the Kundalini, how to put it at the Sahasrara,
这样提升昆达里尼 怎样把它安放在顶轮

213
00:15:23,583 --> 00:15:27,792
how to break the Sahasrara, all these things you must know,
怎样突破顶轮 所有这些事情你必须知道

214
00:15:28,000 --> 00:15:32,667
how to spend your knowledge is viniyoga in Sanskrit.
怎样传播你的知识 在梵语里是 viniyoga 

215
00:15:33,792 --> 00:15:37,625
Guru principle is awakened in a person
导师原理在一个人内在被唤醒

216
00:15:37,875 --> 00:15:39,917
when he himself has achieved something.
当他自己已经达成了一些事

217
00:15:40,166 --> 00:15:44,291
Imagine a half-baked guru going along talking as a Guru.
想象一下一个半生不熟的导师像一个导师一样一直说话

218
00:15:44,583 --> 00:15:49,000
He'll end up as a disciple ultimately.
他将最终以一个门徒的身份而终结

219
00:15:50,166 --> 00:15:51,959
So you have to be master of your own,
因此你必须要成为你自己的主人

220
00:15:52,166 --> 00:15:54,500
but when the Guru Principle comes in
但是当导师原理达成

221
00:15:54,709 --> 00:15:56,500
you have to give it to others,
你要把它给予他人

222
00:15:56,709 --> 00:15:59,625
it's a question of giving it to others.
给予他人这是一个问题

223
00:15:59,834 --> 00:16:04,333
So you have to be at a higher level to give it to others,
因此你要达到一个更高的水平 去给予他人

224
00:16:05,625 --> 00:16:08,000
have to be at a very high level.
要达到一个非常高的水平

225
00:16:08,333 --> 00:16:10,583
If you are attached to money, if you are attached to food,
如果你执着于金钱 如果你执着于食物

226
00:16:10,792 --> 00:16:15,208
if you are attached to mundane things of life, you cannot give.
如果你执着于生活中世俗的事情 你就不能给予

227
00:16:17,125 --> 00:16:22,583
Now the higher state than that can be achieved,
现在更高的境界可以达成

228
00:16:23,417 --> 00:16:27,208
which is naturally in Me, but can be achieved,
那自然地在我内在 但是是可以达成

229
00:16:27,542 --> 00:16:33,375
is that you don't have to have any dependence like that,
那就是你不用像那样有任何依赖

230
00:16:33,750 --> 00:16:36,917
that any rules and regulations,
那任何的规则和规矩

231
00:16:37,166 --> 00:16:41,583
like saying that I will have no worry about food,
就像说我将对食物没有任何担忧

232
00:16:41,875 --> 00:16:43,500
I should fast, this, that -
我要禁食 这样 那样

233
00:16:43,709 --> 00:16:49,417
it all ends up. When you eat but don't eat,
所有的都完结 当你吃或不吃

234
00:16:50,625 --> 00:16:53,667
that's the state one should have,
那就是你要达到的境界

235
00:16:53,917 --> 00:16:57,375
that you are eating the food
那就是你在吃食物

236
00:16:57,834 --> 00:17:01,792
and if you ask, "Did you have your lunch?"
如果你问 你吃了午餐吗

237
00:17:02,083 --> 00:17:04,792
"I don't know ..."
我不知道

238
00:17:06,125 --> 00:17:08,125
"Will you have your lunch?"
你要吃午餐吗

239
00:17:08,333 --> 00:17:10,959
"I don't know ..."
我不知道

240
00:17:11,166 --> 00:17:17,125
Absolutely indifferent to the problems of the body.
完全对身体的问题漠不关心

241
00:17:18,291 --> 00:17:20,166
"Where did you sleep?"
你在哪里睡觉

242
00:17:20,375 --> 00:17:23,291
"I don't know ..."
我不知道

243
00:17:25,709 --> 00:17:27,667
"What did you eat, what will you have?"
你吃了什么 你会有什么

244
00:17:27,917 --> 00:17:30,542
"I don't know ..."
我不知道

245
00:17:30,875 --> 00:17:35,291
This kind of a state is called ateeta state where you go beyond
这种类型的境界叫做ateeta 境界你要超越到那里

246
00:17:35,667 --> 00:17:40,500
and whatever you do, you are doing it
无论你做什么 你就是在做

247
00:17:40,875 --> 00:17:44,417
because it is to be done. Without paying any attention to it,
因为它就是要完成 不放任何注意力

248
00:17:44,750 --> 00:17:47,000
is automatic.
就是自动的

249
00:17:47,208 --> 00:17:51,834
Nothing is important, but this is -
没有什么是重要的 但是这个是

250
00:17:52,125 --> 00:17:55,208
before becoming ateeta you have to tell yourself,
在成为 ateeta之前 你要告诉你自己

251
00:17:55,417 --> 00:17:57,417
"Nothing is important," you see, is a, avir bhava
什么都不重要 你看 就是 avir bhava

252
00:17:57,625 --> 00:18:01,999
they call it, is a kind of a drama you have to put in.
他们称它 是一种戏剧你要把它放进去

253
00:18:02,166 --> 00:18:05,041
"Oh, nothing is important, this carpet is not important,
噢 没有什么是重要的 这些地毯不重要

254
00:18:05,250 --> 00:18:07,917
I should try to sleep on the cement."
我应该尝试在水泥地上睡觉

255
00:18:08,125 --> 00:18:10,583
First you have to do that.
首先你要那样做

256
00:18:10,959 --> 00:18:13,458
But after some time it happens
但是一段时间以后 就会发生这样的事

257
00:18:13,667 --> 00:18:16,291
that you don't remember whether you slept on the cement
你就不记得是否睡在水泥地上了

258
00:18:16,542 --> 00:18:20,583
or on a cot, "Where did I sleep? I don't know."
或者在一个简易床上 我睡在哪里的 我不知道

259
00:18:20,917 --> 00:18:23,999
That is the ateeta state.
那就是ateeta境界

260
00:18:26,750 --> 00:18:32,291
And that state is to be achieved now by many Sahaja Yogis-
那种境界 现在需要很多霎哈嘉瑜伽仕去达成

261
00:18:32,750 --> 00:18:35,750
in a state where you go beyond.
在一种超越的状态中

262
00:18:36,083 --> 00:18:40,500
Say there is somebody who is before you and you have to get angry.
假设有一些人在你面前 你生气了

263
00:18:40,792 --> 00:18:44,000
All right, you give them left, right, left, right nicely
好的 你给他们左一巴掌 右一巴掌 左一巴掌 右一巴掌 非常好

264
00:18:44,250 --> 00:18:48,000
and then you are smiling next moment.
然后下一刻你就笑了

265
00:18:48,375 --> 00:18:52,917
Did you get angry with that person? "I don't know, did I?"
你对那个人发火了吗 我不知道 我发火了吗

266
00:18:55,709 --> 00:18:59,667
Like Buddha once said something
就像佛陀有一次说了什么

267
00:19:00,250 --> 00:19:03,041
in one village
在一个小村庄

268
00:19:03,250 --> 00:19:05,041
and there was a horrible fellow who got up
那有一个可怕的家伙 他站起来了

269
00:19:05,250 --> 00:19:07,959
and said lots of things to him.
然后对佛陀说了很多

270
00:19:08,458 --> 00:19:10,709
And when He went to the next village the fellow felt
然后当他去下一个村庄的时候 那个家伙感觉

271
00:19:10,917 --> 00:19:14,750
that "Oh, I should not have done that," Left Vishuddi, perhaps.
噢 我不应该那样做 左喉轮 有可能

272
00:19:15,208 --> 00:19:18,000
So he went down and said, "I am sorry Sir, I have said so
因此他就蹲下说 先生 我错了 我说了那些

273
00:19:18,208 --> 00:19:19,792
and I should not have said it,
而我就不应该说

274
00:19:19,999 --> 00:19:21,542
I didn't know You are the enlightened one,
我不知道你就是那个觉醒的人

275
00:19:21,750 --> 00:19:23,250
so it happened, so forgive me."
所以我那样做了 请原谅我吧

276
00:19:23,458 --> 00:19:26,166
He said "When, where did you say?"
他说 什么时候 你在什么地方说的

277
00:19:26,959 --> 00:19:28,125
He said, "In the last village."
他说 在上一个村庄

278
00:19:28,333 --> 00:19:30,583
"Oh, everything in the last village I have left there alone
哦 所有的都是在上一个村庄啊 我已经把它们单独留在那里了

279
00:19:30,792 --> 00:19:33,625
and I don't trouble with it."
我也没觉得烦恼

280
00:19:34,625 --> 00:19:37,375
That is the ateeta state that you have to reach.
那就是你要达到的ateeta的境界

281
00:19:37,667 --> 00:19:42,125
So even not to feel, it's not important.
因此 甚至是不用感觉 它一点都不重要

282
00:19:42,625 --> 00:19:46,834
These identifications when they drop out completely
这样的认同当他们完全脱离

283
00:19:47,208 --> 00:19:52,792
then you are doing things in akarma state,
然后你做事情就在akarma 境界中

284
00:19:53,250 --> 00:19:58,375
where, like sun is shining it doesn't know it is shining.
那里 像太阳发光 它并不知道它在发光

285
00:19:58,875 --> 00:20:01,667
When the vibrations are flowing you don't know it is flowing.
当能量在流动 你不知道它在流动

286
00:20:01,959 --> 00:20:04,208
Already it has started working in you.
它已经开始在你身上运作了

287
00:20:04,458 --> 00:20:06,792
You are surprised, you raise the hands and the Kundalini is rising.
你很吃惊 你抬起你的手 昆达里尼就升起来了

288
00:20:07,000 --> 00:20:09,999
You don't know you are raising the Kundalini actually.
你实际上不知道你提升了昆达里尼

289
00:20:10,417 --> 00:20:12,834
How do you raise it?
你怎样提升它的

290
00:20:13,333 --> 00:20:16,208
You don't know, that's it.
你不知道 那就是了

291
00:20:18,792 --> 00:20:21,333
That state has already started ateeta in you,
那样的境界ateeta已经在你内在运作了

292
00:20:21,542 --> 00:20:24,166
but get it established in every walk of life,
但是要建立它在生活中的每一步

293
00:20:24,375 --> 00:20:29,041
everything, that you go beyond.
每一件事 你要超越

294
00:20:30,583 --> 00:20:34,083
And if you can manage that,
而如果你可以处理它

295
00:20:35,166 --> 00:20:38,291
that's the highest that you have to reach.
那就是你要达成的最高境界

296
00:20:43,999 --> 00:20:47,959
Now with the incarnations it's very different,
对于化身来说 是非常不同的

297
00:20:48,208 --> 00:20:50,166
it's the other way round.
是相反的

298
00:20:50,375 --> 00:20:52,834
Everything is the other way round.
所有的一切都是相反的

299
00:20:53,000 --> 00:20:56,959
They don't have to do any tapasya.
他们不需要做任何的苦行

300
00:20:58,000 --> 00:21:01,500
They don't have to starve, they don't have to cleanse themselves,
他们不需要挨饿 他们不需要清理他们自己

301
00:21:01,792 --> 00:21:06,458
whatever they do is the punya.
他们做什么事都是punya福德

302
00:21:06,999 --> 00:21:09,083
They don't have to collect punyas either.
他们根本都不需要积累福德

303
00:21:09,291 --> 00:21:12,959
If they kill somebody it is dharma.
如果他们杀了某个人 它就是正法

304
00:21:13,250 --> 00:21:15,291
If they hit somebody it is the dharma.
如果他们打了某个人 它就是正法

305
00:21:15,583 --> 00:21:19,000
Nothing they do wrong.
他们没有做错任何事

306
00:21:19,333 --> 00:21:22,208
They are absolutely immaculate.
他们是完全完美的

307
00:21:22,709 --> 00:21:25,750
If they deceive someone, they cheat someone,
如果他们蒙蔽某人 他们欺骗某人

308
00:21:25,959 --> 00:21:28,250
it's perfectly all right.
他是完全完美的

309
00:21:28,500 --> 00:21:34,041
Because for a higher goal you have to give up the smaller goals.
因为为了更高的目标你要放弃那些小目标

310
00:21:35,041 --> 00:21:38,125
It's justified in our day-to-day life you'll see,
你会看到在我们的日常生活中 这被调整

311
00:21:38,417 --> 00:21:40,959
that when you are defending your country,
当你防护你的国家

312
00:21:41,125 --> 00:21:44,250
there is an enemy on you, if you have to defend your country
那有一个你们的敌人 如果你要防护你的国家

313
00:21:44,500 --> 00:21:46,875
you cannot slay him.
你不能杀害他

314
00:21:47,208 --> 00:21:51,834
You can cheat him, diplomatically you can befool him.
你可以欺骗他 你可以圆滑地愚弄他

315
00:21:52,083 --> 00:21:53,667
Is allowed, why?
这是允许的 为什么

316
00:21:53,875 --> 00:21:58,083
Because for a higher goal you have to give up the smaller goal.
因为为了一个更高的目标你要放弃小的目标

317
00:21:58,291 --> 00:22:00,875
But for an incarnation it is always the higher goal.
但是对于一个化身来说 这总是有更高的目标

318
00:22:01,125 --> 00:22:04,250
He is not bothered about smaller goals at all.
